title: Kraft Bags With Window, Kraft Sealable Pouches, Kraft Pouches With Window, Sealable Brown Bags, Applicable for Nuts, Coffee Beans, Tea Leaves, Spices, etc. (10x15cm 100PCS)
features: KRAFT POUCHES SIZE : The size of the kraft bags with window is 10x15cm. There are 100pcs kraft sealable pouches per pack, You can put all kinds of nuts, candies, coffee beans, etc in these kraft pouches with window.

HIGH QUALITY MATERIAL : Kraft bags with window outer layer is waterproof film, middle layer is kraft paper, food grade membrane attached to the inner layer. You can use an oil-based pen to record the contents on a kraft sealable pouches.

UNIQUE DESIGN : Kraft bags with window opening can be sealed by heat sealing machine, U-shaped notch at the top of the bag, easy to tear after heat sealing. Kraft sealable pouches body has a transparent window, you can view the items stored in the bag directly.

WIDE RANGE OF APPLICATIONS : Kraft bags with window perfect for storing well-dried food, nuts, candy, coffee beans, grains, snacks, seeds, beans and dehydrated herbs, etc. Kraft sealable pouches is suitable for Christmas, Halloween, Mother's Day, Easter, events such as party, birthdays , weddings.

EXCELLENT CUSTOMER SERVICE : If you find the kraft bags with window broken and damaged, do not use it and replace it with a new one. Please contact our customer service department for a free replacement kraft sealable pouches or refund.
